article.description: — Trey Woodbury had 22 points in Utah Valley's 73-69 win against Northern Arizona on Saturday night.
article.headline: Utah Valley earns 73-69 win against Northern Arizona
article.linkText: Utah Valley earns 73-69 win against Northern Arizona
article.story: OREM, Utah -- — Trey Woodbury had 22 points in Utah Valley's 73-69 win against Northern Arizona on Saturday night. Woodbury added six assists for the Wolverines (2-1). Aziz Bandaogo scored 13 points and added 12 rebounds and four blocks. Le'Tre Darthard recorded 13 points and was 5 of 8 shooting (3 for 6 from distance). Jack Wistrcill led the way for the Lumberjacks (0-3) with 14 points and six rebounds. Liam Lloyd added 14 points and two steals for Northern Arizona. Oakland Fort also had 12 points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
